Description: Here goes the story. Purchase this year's back in for attempts to bring her back to her glory. But time is taking over and it's time for this guitar to go to somebody with much more time than I do. So here goes a awesome what used to be and what was a custom shop instrument. Guitar is tele shaped with a beautiful flame Maple neck no structural issues that I can see. One thing of note is at the body was routed for a Floyd at one time and looks like it was blocked off and refinished I believe. There is body dings dents scratches throughout. Please check out the photographs the guitars being sold as a project as is sold no returns. Also to know that there's a bit of paint chipping around the tone pot which appear to have been opened a little bit for some big pots please check out the photographs. Guitars being sold as a project as is no returns. This was once a $3,000 guitar years back it's time for her to go back to making music. Also the guitar will come with a very cool Fender advertisement that I just found right about the time of the listing.. Also there are no pickups. And I'm not sure what parts are there are not there. I believe everything should be there minus the pickups maybe the switch tip. Also that mead binder is not included in this auction. I needed hit the keep all the parts together for the picture..
Title: 1989 Roger SADOWSKY NYC Type T Hand Built flame maple fender hm ad telecaster
